 Burna Boy‘s fans have continued to react to the warning he issued last night at his live Lagos concert. During his performance, the self-proclaimed ‘Odogwu’ abruptly came to a halt, urging some of his supporters to refrain from climbing on stage. READ ALSO: I pledge to be the cause of joy to everyone I meet for the rest of my life – Burna Boy I know it’s love, he explained, but love can enter your body and cause you to jump on stage and do things like that because I don’t know your intentions, it took me a long time to adjust. He said: “I know it is love, the love can enter your body and you jump on stage and things like that. It took me a long time to get used to it because I don’t know your intentions”.